<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include ('./partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/forms.css" />
    <script src="/script/forms.js"></script>
    <script src="/script/register.js"></script>
    <script src="/script/validations/registerValidation.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include ('./partials/header') %>

    <main class="form-main">

      <section class="section-form">
        
        <div class="bg-light-blue br-10">

            <% if(locals.errors){ errors.forEach(error => {%>
              <p class="font-navy"><%= error.msg %></p>
            <% }) } %>
          
          <form class="form" action="/usuarios/registro" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
          <h2 class="w-100">Registrate</h2>

          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
            <input class="form-inp" type="text" name="first_name" id="first_name" placeholder="Nombre" value="<%= locals.old && old.firstName ? old.firstName : ''%>" />
          </div>
          <span class="w-100 text-center" id="spanFirstName"></span>

          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input class="form-inp" type="text" name="last_name" id="last_name" placeholder="Apellido" value="<%= locals.old && old.lastName ? old.lastName : ''%>" />
          </div>
          <span class="w-100 text-center" id="spanLastName"></span>

          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input class="form-inp" type="mail" placeholder="Correo electrónico" name="email" id="email" value="<%= locals.old && old.email ? old.email : ''%>" />
          </div>
          <span class="w-100 text-center" id="spanEmail"></span>

          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input class="form-inp" type="number" name="dni" id="dni" placeholder="Documento" value="<%= locals.old && old.dni ? old.dni : ''%>" />
          </div>
          <span class="w-100 text-center" id="spanDni"></span>
          
          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input class="form-inp" type="text" name="address" id="address" placeholder="Domicilio" value="<%= locals.old && old.address ? old.address : ''%>"/>
          </div>
          <span class="w-100 text-center" id="spanAddress"></span>

          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
            <input class="form-inp" type="date" name="birthdate" id="birthdate" value="<%= locals.old && old.birthdate ? old.birthdate : ''%>" />
          </div>

          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input class="form-inp" type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="Contraseña" size="15" maxlength="64"/>
          </div>
          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <progress max="100" value="0" id="meter"></progress>
              <span id="spanPassword"></span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex fx-wrap w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <label for="profile_image" class="w-100">Imagen de Perfil:</label>
              <div class="w-100 p-8">
                <input type="file" name="profile_image" id="profile_image" />
              </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <div class="form-inp flex">
                <input class="w-25" type="checkbox" required />
                <p class="w-75" for="checkpoint">
                  Al continuar, doy fe de entender y aceptar la política de
                  privacidad, los términos y condiciones y los términos de uso
                  del sitio web. Al clickear “únete ahora” reconozco aceptar
                  formar parte del programa de beneficios de Take off Surf y
                  recibir ofertas exclusivas en mi correo electrónico. Puede
                  desuscibirse en cualquier momento clickeando elboton
                  “desuscribir” ubicado en el final de los correos electrónicos
                  recibidos.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <button class="form-button" type="submit" id="submit">Enviar</button>
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <button class="form-button" type="reset">Resetear</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include ('./partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>